Third-party attributions
=========================

Minisforum / AtomMan (SCCS.exe)
-------------------------------
The panel serial protocol and the vendor embedded-controller register map were
reverse-engineered from the vendor's Windows driver (SCCSetup.exe -> SCCS.exe)
for interoperability with hardware the user owns. No vendor code is included or
redistributed in this repository; this is an original, independent
reimplementation.
